| Concept          | Key Point                                                    |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Stack            | Automatic allocation, fast, function-local variables         |
| Heap             | Dynamic allocation using `new`, manual cleanup with `delete` |
| Memory Leak      | Allocated memory not released                                |
| Dangling Pointer | Pointer to freed memory                                      |
| Wild Pointer     | Uninitialized pointer                                        |
| Null Pointer     | `nullptr`, points to nothing                                 |
